title: Beowulf (DC - The New 52)
description:
2 CBRs | English | 39+21 pages

The New 52 Beowulf (Sword of Sorcery #0-3 backups & DCU Presents #19)
Written by Tony Bedard
Art by Jesus Saiz with Brian Reber (SoS backups) & Javier Pina with Jason Wright 

Beowulf made his New 52 debut in Sword and Sorcery #0 in September 2012 as a back up feature. The character was re-imagined into post-apocalyptic setting with remnants of advanced technology visible among the medieval setting. He then later gained a one-shot feature in DC Universe Presents #19.

This torrent compiles the SoS backups of the first four issues into 1 CBR and DC Universe Presents #19.
